To build and install pstocanonij:

  1) Building misc libraries.
        cd ../libs
        ./autogen.sh
        make
        cd ../pstocanonij
   


  2) Building "pstocanonij".
        ./autogen.sh
        make
        make install


     Appendix:
        * You can also set the following options.
           --prefix

           --enable-progpath
                cif(ex.cifip4600)

     Example:
           ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --enable-progpath=/usr/local/bin
           make
           make install

